  in  fact  this  is  an  important  act  that encourages workers engaged in the organized sector  workers in our country are lowest  paid  but  our  government  has  felt  the  pain  of  those  workers    it  is  a praiseworthy step that those workers who were earlier excluded from the eligibility criteria  of  getting  bonus  would  be  now  eligible  to  get  bonus    government  has considered the memorandums and suggestions made by trade unions and has taken decision  in  the  interest  of  workers  that  present  ceiling  limit  with  regard  to  bonus would be implemented wef 1st april 2000    